snippet.title: RAID: Shadow Legends | In Treatment | Galek - Who am I? (Official Commercial)
snippet.description:
Who said Champions with big teeth can’t get therapy?

Ignore the potential of your Champions and they might go off the
deep end. Build them up and you might save them some soul
searching.

With 1+ million Champion builds in RAID, you decide!
